title: Enkei wheels, lengthened axle tubes, windows, backing.

posts.content:
All parts have been removed from my 64 Splitty, for info and pics email me at skemp75@yahoo.co.uk or phone me on 07917897757

Original windows, door tops have been sold so 9 are left. 2 are side pop outs with arms and all are in good condition with some old Skool stickers on them. Looking for £150 Ono and could possibly post or even deliver if the price is right.

Enkei wide 5 x 205 PCD, 3 are in really good condition with good tyres and one has some small stains on the paint work and a small ding on the rim with a worn tyre, can be re furbed for about £50 though. Looking for £300 Ono and can post.SOLD

Axle tubes for straight axle conversion, these have been lengthened, blasted, etched and painted satin black. Has some pitting in the metal but in good usable condition, comes with rubber boots, looking for £100 Ono and can post.SOLD

Rear spring plates stock, blasted, etched and painted satin black. looking for £30 Ono and can post.

Rear brake backing plates, sightless pitted but have been blasted, etched and painted satin black, looking for £30 and can post.SOLD

You got a picture of the wheels bud?

Also interested in the pop outs!
